umber and email.&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Please also rea</span>d our Auction Consignment Agreement&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">or call us at +852-3168 2192 for further information.</span>&nbsp;</p>', '<h1 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif;\"><b>委託拍賣</b></h1><div style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;</div><div style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">為在來屆拍賣會呈獻更多珍貴藏品予全球收藏家， 我們正進行全球性拍品徵集活動。</div><div style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">&nbsp;</div><div style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\"><img src=\"http://lhauction.com.hk/site_upload/userfiles/%E5%BE%B5%E9%9B%86_small.jpg\" _fcksavedurl=\"/site_upload/userfiles/徵集_small.jpg\" width=\"650\" height=\"420\" alt=\"\"></div><div style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\"><p>&nbsp;</p><h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span lang=\"ZH-HK\" style=\"font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">徵集日程</span><o:p></o:p></h1><h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">馬來西亞吉隆坡站 – 2017年12月8日-12日</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">中國深圳站 – 2017年12月14日-18日</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span lang=\"ZH-HK\" style=\"font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">更多行程敬請關注仕宏拍賣官方網站或微信公眾號</span><o:p></o:p></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(142, 26, 29);\">徵集項目：<br>古董名茶 | 茶具花器 | 中國書畫 | 名人手跡 | 古董珍玩 | 沉香奇楠 |</span></p><p>仕宏拍賣自2013年成立至今，成為香港藏茶界知名的專業古董名茶葉拍賣公司，曾創下以<strong>逾1,000萬港元成交一筒百年藍標宋聘圓茶</strong>的紀錄；於2017年春季拍賣之古董級普洱茶專場總成交價破3,800萬港元，為茶葉拍賣市場立下彪炳紀錄。希望藉本次現場徵集活動，與藏家增進溝通，推廣茶文化至全球各地。<br>我們的專家團隊將會為您提供免費的估值服務。</p><p>如欲參與或透過微信或電郵委託拍賣或諮詢，歡迎將委託拍賣珍藏品的資料、新舊狀況及相關圖片，連同個人聯絡資料（姓名、聯絡電話、電郵、微信號等）電郵至&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:auction@lh-hk.com\" _fcksavedurl=\"mailto:auction@lh-hk.com\"><span style=\"color: rgb(204, 0, 0);\">auction@lh-hk.com</span></a>&nbsp;，或直接致電+852-3168 2192 / +86 158 1858 1118 洽談委託拍賣事宜，仕宏拍賣專家會為您提供免費估價及市場諮詢服務，歡迎廣大藏家踴躍參與。</p><p>賣家亦可參閱拍賣目錄內的拍賣品委託合約或致電+852 3168 2192查詢有關詳情。</p></div>', 'admin', '1512364483', null, '1', null, '', '', ''), ('4', 'about', '公司簡介', '7', 'http://dev.curio.com/public/content/img/1512365150.jpg', '<p style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(204, 0, 51);\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: larger;\"><span style=\"line-height: 18px;\">About L&amp;H Auction Co., Ltd.</span></span></span></strong></p><p style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">Established in 2013, L&amp;H Auction Co. Ltd. is a young yet fast-growing auctioneer based in Hong Kong. L&amp;H held its first photographica auction in June 2013, focusing on the world’s rarest and finest antique cameras, the famous German Leica. During the 2014 Spring Auction, L&amp;H has achieved a total of over HK$39 millions. Receording great successes in consecutive sales, L&amp;H has soon become one of the most important auctioneers of vintage cameras in the world.</p><p style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">Witnessing the immense demand from collectors and antique lovers, L &amp; H has developed its interest to other extensive specialty areas with connoisseurship and professionalism, including but not limited to Vintage Pu-er Tea, Classical Chinese Paintings, Agarwood and Qinan, Japanese Tea wares and Vessels, Wine and Spirits, Ceramics and other Chinese works of art.</p><p style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">L&amp;H’s biannual sales series in Hong Kong are held in May and November. Biddings can be made in person, by telephone, mail, e-mail or fax. In addition, bidders can watch our live auction through internet and place biddings once the sale starts.</p><p style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(204, 0, 51);\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: larger;\"><span style=\"line-height: 18px;\">Mission</span></span></span></strong></p><p style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">The objective of the auctioneer is to showcase a variety of antique items and prized collections to the wide public.&nbsp;L&amp;H values fine objects from every culture and time period and&nbsp;strives to provide extraordinary services to clients.</p>', '<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: larger;\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(204, 0, 51);\"><span style=\"line-height: 18px; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">關於仕宏拍賣有限公司</span></strong></span></h2><p style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">以香港為基地的仕宏拍賣有限公司成立於2013年，秉承「仕以高品而宏」之專業態度及宗旨，力求為收藏興趣愈益多元化的藏家們提供炙手可熱的藏品，將旗下拍賣活動打造成為收藏家們搜尋頂級珍品的良機盛會。</p><p style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">作為亞洲區舉辦專業相機拍賣的先鋒及佼佼者，仕宏第三屆珍稀相機拍賣會總成交額逾三千九百萬港元，在短短兩年間已躍升為全球同類專門相機拍賣行的第二位。</p><p style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">於2014年開始更引入中國書畫﹑奇楠沉香﹑古董普洱名茶及御器等專場拍賣，成為香港藏茶界知名的專業古董名茶葉拍賣公司，曾創下以逾1,000萬港元成交一筒百年藍標宋聘圓茶的紀錄；於2017年春季拍賣之古董級普洱茶專場總成交價破3,800萬港元，為茶葉拍賣市場立下彪炳紀錄。在提供專業拍賣服務的同時，也積極投身于相關文化的發展及傳播中。以多層次的管道向大中華地區提供優質藏品及國際尖端資訊，遵循「高品質，高品味，高誠信度」的服務原則，為廣大藏家打造「可宏高仕之志」的不二平臺。</p><p style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">除親臨拍賣會場﹑電話競投及信件﹑傳真﹑電子郵件委託競投外，競投者亦可在世界各地於網上觀看拍賣直播及同步參與競投。</p>', 'admin', '1512365151', '1512365346', '1', '1', '', '', ''), ('5', 'contact', '聯絡我們', '8', 'http://dev.curio.com/public/content/img/1512365174.jpg', '<p style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(142, 26, 29);\">L&amp;H Auction Co., Ltd.</span></strong></p><p style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(142, 26, 29);\">ADDRESS</span>&nbsp;<br>Unit 1207-1208&nbsp;<br>12/F Star House&nbsp;<br>3 Salisbury Road&nbsp;<br>Tsim Sha Ts